lifa Islamiyah Mindanao]], [[Maute Group]]\n*** Advocacy group:[[Bangsamoro Islamic Freedom Fighters|Bangsamoro Islamic Freedom Movement]]<ref name=biffIS />\n[[Cordillera Administrative Region]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Igorot people|Igorot]]\n** Proposed autonomous area: [[Cordillera Autonomous Region]]<ref name=car>{{cite news |title=Cordillera Solons expressed views on regional autonomy |url=http://car.neda.gov.ph/cordillera-solons-expressed-views-on-regional-autonomy/ |accessdate=28 February 2015 |publisher=[[National Economic and Development Authority]] \u2013 Cordillera Administrative Region |date=12 August 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402152317/http://car.neda.gov.ph/cordillera-solons-expressed-views-on-regional-autonomy/ |archive-date=2 April 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref> or [[Autonomous Region of the Cordillera]]<ref>{{cite news |last1=Ponciano |first1=Mark Allen |title=Cordi autonomy bill filed as HB 5343 |url=http://car.neda.gov.ph/cordi-autonomy-bill-filed-hb-5343/ |accessdate=6 October 2017 |work=National Economic and Development Authority \u2013 Cordillera Administrative Region |date=24 March 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719075255/http://car.neda.gov.ph/cordi-autonomy-bill-filed-hb-5343/ |archive-date=19 July 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n** Advocacy group: Autonomy in the Administrative Cordillera Movement,<ref>{{cite news |last1=Dumlao |first1=Artemio |title=Autonomy movement revived in Cordillera |url=http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2014/02/11/1288987/autonomy-movement-revived-cordillera |accessdate=31 August 2017 |work=The Philippine Star |date=11 February 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831090321/http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2014/02/11/1288987/autonomy-movement-revived-cordillera |archive-date=31 August 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref> [[Cordillera People's Liberation Army]]<!---historical armed conflict, now only pushes for autonomy through non-armed means.--->,<ref name=\"rebeldream\